==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: outpope the Pope
<hw>out*pope" the Pope`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To try
to act as a more authentic member of a group than one who is a genuine
member of the group; -- not necessarily in reference to religious
matters; compare <cref>to be more Catholic than the Pope</cref>.</def>
<mark>[Colloq.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Outport</ent>⟦br⟧
